definition: Sansui county in Qiandongnan Miao and Dong autonomous prefecture 黔東南州|黔东南州[Qian2 dong1 nan2 zhou1], Guizhou
abbr. for Guangzhou 廣州|广州[Guang3 zhou1]

sentences.english: It is reported that perpetrators are Qiandongnan Sansui County, called the dragon years strong.
sentences.chinese: 據悉，行兇者是黔東南州三穗縣人，叫龍久烈。

sentences.english: General Yang Zhicheng was born in Sansui county, Guizhou province.
sentences.chinese: 楊至成將軍是貴州省三穗縣八弓鎮木界村侗家人。
